; Regression test for issue #2011: post date not considered for lots
;
; When a posting has a date override via the ; [date] notation, that date
; should be used as the lot acquisition date rather than the transaction date.

2021/01/01 * Buy stocks
    Assets:Stocks  25 AMZN @ $10 ; [2021/01/05]
    Assets:Savings

test bal --lots
               $-250
25 AMZN {$10} [2021/01/05]  Assets
               $-250    Savings
25 AMZN {$10} [2021/01/05]    Stocks
--------------------
               $-250
25 AMZN {$10} [2021/01/05]
end test
